title: Arbor & Flux At Bear Mountain's Hot Dawgz & Hand Rails
description:
Arbor Snowboards and Flux Bindings got together for their first ever collaboration video from Bear Mountain's Hot Dawgz & Hand Rails featuring Ryan Tarbell, Erik Leon, Scotty Vine, Lenny Mazzotti, Chad Tarbell, Uma Abe, and Ian Sams. Congratulations to Ian Sams for taking third place in the event.
Film/Edit: Eli Weiner
